Energy Recovery Products, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg










































  





















































































July 28, 2017 12:28 PM ET
Electrical Equipment

Company Overview of Energy Recovery Products, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Energy Recovery Products, Inc. designs and manufactures AC/DC power supplies. It offers open-frame power supplies, LED drivers, and custom designs. The company’s products are used in LED lighting, industrial, medical, telecom, IT, and computing markets. Energy Recovery Products, Inc. was founded in 2006 and is based in Moorpark, California. The company has a manufacturing location in Zhuhai, China.


301 Science DriveSuite 210Moorpark, CA 93021United StatesFounded in 2006



Phone: 805-517-1300

Fax: 805-517-1411

