Culture of Innovation
Innovation Engine
At Energy Recovery, we pride ourselves on being a hub of innovation. We have put together a team of world-class engineers who come up with new ideas for how we can use our technology to tap unused pressure energy and make industrial processes more profitable, safer, and more efficient.
ISO Certification
As part of our efforts to enhance our operational efficiency, we have completed our ISO 9000 certification, the industry standard for quality management. This will help up continue to meet the needs of our customers and stakeholders in the best, most efficient manner possible.
Ethics and Accountability
Energy Recovery is committed to the highest standards of ethical conduct in its financial affairs and reporting. We offer a confidential, anonymous reporting system dedicated to addressing complaints regarding accounting, internal accounting controls, or auditing matters, as well as violations of our Code of Conduct and Ethics. Learn more
Corporate Culture
Energy Recovery prides itself on having a strong culture that is attractive to employees and customers. This important asset is nurtured by all employees who strive to maintain our unique identity and core values.  We believe our employees feel a sense of pride when they work in an  environment of empowerment, open communication, recognition, inclusion, collaboration, and innovation.
Meet some of our innovators below. Want to join the team?











